# INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.unspecified

**Case**

An unspecified response code.

## Declaration

```swift
case unspecified
```

## Reporting a Problem

- **INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.failure**: Your intent handler is unable to handle the intent.
- **INShareFocusStatusIntentResponseCode.failureRequiringAppLaunch**: The user needs to launch your app to update their focus status.
